{
  "stem": "1062.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was about three years ago, which I'm very proud of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The director is Randolph Braham.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's the director.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well-known man in the Holocaust, in particular the Hungarian Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I am the-- what do you call it-- the benefactor or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I support it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I would tell you I did it because I'm smart, don't believe it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because sometimes people ask me a question, how do you just survive?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I survived because I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't because I planned to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Listen, let me tell you something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you are marching down a column and somebody comes and says, listen, half the column stay over here and half of the column stay over there, and those people who stay over here are machine-gunned, and I don't care how brave you are and how smart you are.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How I survived was sheer luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How I did this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, hard work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll tell you, when I worked-- when I started to work here, even when I got vacation-- I remember when I worked in the factory there in Triangle Steel, when I got vacations-- two weeks a year, I got a vacation-- I went across the street.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lumber yard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got a job at the lumber yard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, it was luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course it was also, of course, you had to have a little brains to know what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's a combination of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's really a combination of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Would I take the credit for all for myself?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course a lot of it had to do with my family too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My wife and my father-in-law, you know, they helped me out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want to take the credit, because it was a combination of things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm lucky, I guess.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a collage which was put together maybe about 20 years ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this here is my village where I came from, Comlaus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As you can see, here are the children sitting in the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when they came home from cheder there was a family who came to America, so they took a picture.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took out those three-- those three boys from here, and I am in the middle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Take a good shot of my shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those are the Gucci Gucci shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Original.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Very seldom we wore shoes, especially in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have shoes in my village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But so-- you can see all the children, no shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this is the village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This here is my youngest brother, Avrum, and this is my sister, Baile.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This here is my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is my grandmother's mother, and this is my grandmother's father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Have I mentioned to you--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm going to repeat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I say, this is my grandmother's mother, Edith.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My grandmother's father, Shloimo Leazar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He died in 1942, because they took away all the fields from him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Nazis took away the fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't take it, so he died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My great-grandmother, she came with me to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This here is a star which we had to wear during the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is not my star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is just a sample of a star which we had to wear during the war before-- before they put us into the ghettos, for the purpose of identification.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Here this is-- in Buchenwald, they used to have their own currency.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is a-- for the SS, Standarten Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is two Reichsmark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For this you could buy maybe a bottle of good water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was-- the currency was only good in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is a magazine which was printed after the war by a German-- by a German company about Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And here, this is me standing up here on this side to your right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's me after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was maybe about a week or two after-- after liberation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were a lot of movie cameras and photographers and paper-- newspapers in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This here is in Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was taken in Bucharest about three months after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you can still see on my very right, on the-- my lips on the right-hand side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was a burn mark from the Nazis when they put in a match in Buchenwald to test whether I am still alive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I told you the story before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was given to us by the American Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This is the liberation paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is proof that we were in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "After I went back to my village and I didn't find nobody alive, I came back and I settled in a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This camp-- I was in many DP camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This camp was called Camp Herzog in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
